Object "docgen_con_test" Interface:
  (Requires Spin2 Language v46)

── Public Constants ──────────────────────────────────────────

  Error Codes:
    SUCCESS, E_TIMEOUT, E_NO_RESPONSE, E_BAD_RESPONSE, E_IO_ERROR
  Driver Modes:
    MODE_NONE, MODE_RAW, MODE_FULL
  Warning Flags:
    CW_NONE, CW_PROBE_FAILED, CW_FEATURE_SUPPORTED
  Conditional Feature Codes:
