── Public Structures ─────────────────────────────────────────

  STRUCT point_t(x, y)
  STRUCT color_t(BYTE r, BYTE g, BYTE b, BYTE a)
  STRUCT pixel_t(point_t pos, color_t color)

── Public Methods ────────────────────────────────────────────

PUB null()
PUB start(pin_base, pin_count) : result
PUB stop()
PUB read(p_buffer, count) : bytes_read
PUB getWarnings() : flags
PUB getMode() : mode

── Constant Details ──────────────────────────────────────────

Error Codes
___________
  SUCCESS       =  0    Operation completed successfully
  E_TIMEOUT     = -1    Device didn't respond in time
  E_NO_RESPONSE = -2    Device not responding
  E_BAD_RESPONSE = -3    Unexpected response from device
  E_IO_ERROR    = -7    General I/O error

Driver Modes
____________
  MODE_NONE = 0
  MODE_RAW  = 1
  MODE_FULL = 2

Warning Flags
_____________
  Warning flags returned by getWarnings().
  These are bitmask values that can be OR'd together.
  CW_NONE              = $00    No warnings
  CW_PROBE_FAILED      = $01    Probe failed at init
  CW_FEATURE_SUPPORTED = $02    Optional feature confirmed

Conditional Feature Codes
_________________________
  BASE_CODE  = 100    Always present
  FINAL_CODE = 300    Always present

Locally Conditional
___________________
  ALWAYS_HERE   = 1    Unconditional
  LOCAL_ENABLED = 2    Locally defined, so included

Overridable Configuration
_________________________
  Maximum number of open connections.
  Override in parent OBJ declaration.
  Memory cost: 128 bytes per connection.
  MAX_CONNECTIONS = 4    Default connection count (user-overridable)

── Structure Details ─────────────────────────────────────────

STRUCT point_t (8 bytes)
________________________
  LONG  x
  LONG  y

  A 2D point with integer coordinates

STRUCT color_t (4 bytes)
________________________
  BYTE  r
  BYTE  g
  BYTE  b
  BYTE  a

  RGB color with alpha channel

STRUCT pixel_t (12 bytes)
_________________________
  point_tpos
  color_tcolor

── Method Details ────────────────────────────────────────────

__________
PUB null()

 This is not a top-level object

_________________________________________
PUB start(pin_base, pin_count) : result

 Start the driver on a new cog

 @param pin_base - First pin number
 @param pin_count - Number of pins to use
 @returns result - Cog ID (0-7) on success, -1 on failure

__________
PUB stop()

 Stop the driver and release the cog

____________________________________
PUB read(p_buffer, count) : bytes_read

 Read data from the device

 @param p_buffer - Pointer to destination buffer
 @param count - Number of bytes to read
 @returns bytes_read - Actual bytes read (0 at EOF)

________________________
PUB getWarnings() : flags

 Get current warning flags (bitmask of CW_* constants)

 @returns flags - Bitmask of active warnings

_____________________
PUB getMode() : mode

 Get current driver mode (MODE_* constant)

 @returns mode - Current mode value
